N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2651.5 - Compliance with rules

State Regulations

The housing and development administration in its
enforcement activities shall apply the requirements of the Multiple Dwelling

Law, and the rules and regulations adopted by the commissioner where
applicable. Notes
